on and other university bills Update your emergency contact information Get the bus schedule   Features for our future students: Read the latest UNT headlines with “What’s New” Get information about UNT “Admissions” See your list of “To Dos” to stay on track to apply or enroll Check out our “Course Catalog” to see what courses UNT offers Learn about all the ways we can help you pay for college Search for specific classes with the app’s “Class Search” See today’s, this week’s, this weekend’s or this month’s “Calendar” for events and important dates Get familiar with campus before you get here with the app’s “Maps” feature Sign up to “Take a Tour” of campus Read the latest UNT “Sports” headlines Request more information about UNT Learn about UNT’s “Traditions” Features coming this spring for future students: View your admissions status Accept admittance Need Help?Contact the UNT Helpdesk Top Main Menu Home University Links MyUNT Blackboard EagleConnect UNT Directory UNT Map Jobs at UNT Email & Phone  urcm@unt.edu  940-565-2108 UNT Mobile App   University Services Building (USB)   2310 S Interstate 35 E Denton, Texas 76205   Visitor Information Call us Email Us UNT Map Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links | UNT Home ©2017 University of North Texas Required Links 